    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated S54 inline-six. This engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, while the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been meticulously maintained or addressed preventatively. The exterior retains its factory luster with no discernible imperfections, reflecting its sheltered history.",
